{"pid":"7b705050eb9ae9113cec2bd1fff412cd027315ba","tid":2396864,"uid":372390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"低級打工仔有層幾百萬既私樓自住又唔見班同事會眼超超<br />\n一隻勞值幾錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cde8d27079f33bfc6aa0ccd51ae414717ca539e","tid":2396864,"uid":18395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大老細幾百億身家 戴apple watch<br />\n唔通其他人剩係戴膠錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e10a8d89b5d38df4428ad059fcbec9d6dde498","tid":2396864,"uid":147031,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7b705050eb9ae9113cec2bd1fff412cd027315ba","tid":2396864,"uid":372390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"低級打工仔有層幾百萬既私樓自住又唔見班同事會眼超超<br />\n一隻勞值幾錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"仲有私樓幾百萬? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de04f4d85d04d21b46c4d05a809d62c764d5ac7f","tid":2396864,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"關鍵字：蓋清 假撈"},{"pid":"aecd769abe5f61a4b0e154843eb848b63cdc61dc","tid":2396864,"uid":199479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cde8d27079f33bfc6aa0ccd51ae414717ca539e","tid":2396864,"uid":18395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大老細幾百億身家 戴apple watch<br />\n唔通其他人剩係戴膠錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"老闆戴series 6 咁其他人咪戴series 5囉"}]}